  - bias audit
  - machine learning
abstract: "This repository contains supporting files for a gene/protein-level Type 2 Diabetes candidate prioritization study using sequence-derived protein and genomic representations with repeated cross-validation, fusion comparison, leakage/bias auditing, Top-K ranking utility analysis, and biological validation."
